# Component Structure (Web)

## Page Pattern

Every feature page: **Page → Provider → Container**

```
web/src/pages/FeatureNamePage/
├── FeatureNamePage.tsx
├── FeatureNamePageContainer/
├── context/
│   ├── FeatureNamePageProvider.tsx   # orchestrates hooks only
│   └── hooks/
│       ├── api/useFetchFeaturePageData.ts
│       ├── useFeaturePageHandlers.ts
│       ├── useFeaturePageEffects.ts
│       └── useFeaturePageContext.ts
```

## MUST Follow

1. Providers orchestrate hooks only — no `useState`, `useSelector`, or `useEffect` in providers.
2. Containers consume context — early return for loading/error.
3. Named exports; handler prefix `handle`; interface prefix `I`.

## NEVER Do

- NEVER put business logic in providers
- NEVER duplicate RTK Query data in local `useState`
- NEVER use class components (except `ErrorBoundary`)

